dev.strwbry.eventhorizon.events.effects.BaseEffects
dev.strwbry.eventhorizon.events.effects.YoureTooSlow
public class YoureTooSlow extends BaseEffects
Event that gives players a movement-reducing slowness effect. This event applies a level 2 slowness effect for 6000 ticks (5 minutes), making players move significantly slower than normal.
